Package com.circa.mrv.grs_manager.document

Class Order

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.circa.mrv.grs_manager.document.Document
      • com.circa.mrv.grs_manager.document.Order
  • public class Order
extends Document
    An Order class specifies the data and methods for an order that a company will place with a vendor. It has a creation date, delivery date for requested goods, the id of the user who created the order, and the product being ordered. The Order class extends the Document class.
    Author:
    Arthur Vargas
